<plot>After forty years of captivity, 'Perchance To Dream' offers a new perspective in the life of Miami Sea Aquarium's star performer, Lolita the Killer Whale. Brutally taken from her family and home waters in Puget Sound, Washington and flown across the country to live in Miami, Florida, Lolita is expected to perform daily to an enthusiastic crowd; a crowd completely ignorant to the plight of her gentle spirit.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?428831</url></doc>
